QuestData.Title: Claim Korthun's End
QuestData.Description: The Horde has spies in this area? Darkbreak Cove is nearby, and inside lies the Pincer X2! The Horde must not be allowed anywhere nearby!$b$bSomeone in Darkbreak Cove will want to hear of this... after you finish slaying some more of these dirty Horde spies.
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill 7 Hellscream Seadogs in Korthun's End.
QuestData.RewardText: You did well, $n. We need to be especially wary of Horde attacks right now. The Pincer X2 has plenty of firepower at sea, but in the back of this cave, she is exceptionally vulnerable.
